  7,43,My zosadit all ziarlivsot ich srdce. Rieka flow them they say GOD chvalit for guiding us! My possibly nie guided nie bol GOD guided us. Posol our Lord robit bring truth. They bol vola sa This bol tvoj Raj! Ona zdedit it chrbat tvoj robota
  7,44,dwellers Raj vola sa dwellers Hell My zalozit our Lord's promise bol truth have ona zalozit tvoj Lord's promise bol truth They say Ano announcer them zahlasit GOD's condemnation befallen transgressors
